[3] Michigan (Wexford County)
Date: Fri 20 Dec 2019
Source: 9and10 News [edited]
https://www.9and10news.com/2019/12/20/7-cases-of-whooping-cough-confirmed-in-wexford-co-since-october/


The health department confirmed several cases of whooping cough in northern Michigan. Seven cases have been confirmed in Wexford County since October [2019]. They say a number of other cases were reported in surrounding counties.

The health department says that number is likely to rise as lab results come in, along with more reports from the community.

[Byline: Chris Clor]

